name: Street
description:
"Street"
memotret setelah hujan sangatlah mengasik kan, banyak momen-momen yang bisa di tangkap. salah satunya foto yang saya ambil setelah hujan turun, di sebuah gang yang rame akan masyarakat.

photographing after the rain is very fun, there are many moments that can be captured. one of them is a photo that I took after it rained, in an alley that was crowded with people.
